[{"id":"VH935665","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">If <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"b sub n\"><math alttext=\"b sub n\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is a sequence of real numbers with <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"n equal to 0, comma 1, comma 2, comma dot dot dot\"><math alttext=\"n equal to 0, comma 1, comma 2, comma dot dot dot\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>…</mo></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"a, sub n, equals, b sub n, minus, b sub n minus 1, end subscript\"><math alttext=\"a, sub n, equals, b sub n, minus, b sub n minus 1, end subscript\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mrow><mi>b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mrow><mi>b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> for <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"n equals 1, comma 2, comma dot dot dot\"><math alttext=\"n equals 1, comma 2, comma dot dot dot\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>…</mo></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> , which of the following is true about the infinite series <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the sum, from n equals 1, to infinity of, a, sub n\"><math alttext=\"the sum, from n equals 1, to infinity of, a, sub n\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><munderover><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" mathsize=\"140%\"><mrow><mo>∑</mo></mrow></mstyle><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>∞</mi></mrow></munderover><msub><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> ?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH935665_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The series converges if <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the limit as n approaches infinity, of, a, sub n, equals 0\"><math alttext=\"the limit as n approaches infinity, of, a, sub n, equals 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><munder><mrow><mi>lim</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow></munder><msub><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The series converges if <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the limit as n approaches infinity, of, b sub n\"><math alttext=\"the limit as n approaches infinity, of, b sub n\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><munder><mrow><mi>lim</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow></munder><msub><mrow><mi>b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is a finite real number.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The series diverges if <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the limit as n approaches infinity, of, b sub n, is not equal to 0\"><math alttext=\"the limit as n approaches infinity, of, b sub n, is not equal to 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><munder><mrow><mi>lim</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>∞</mi></mrow></munder><msub><mrow><mi>b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow></msub><mo>≠</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The series has <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the limit as n approaches infinity, of, b sub n\"><math alttext=\"the limit as n approaches infinity, of, b sub n\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><munder><mrow><mi>l